import{supabase}from'./supabase';export async function createQualityParameters(data){return supabase.from('quality_parameters').insert([data]);}export async function getQualityParameters(fabricEntryId){return supabase.from('quality_parameters').select('*').eq('fabric_entry_id',fabricEntryId).single();}export async function updateQualityParameters(id,data){return supabase.from('quality_parameters').update(data).eq('id',id);}export async function deleteQualityParameters(id){return supabase.from('quality_parameters').delete().eq('id',id);}export async function getFabricEntryById(id){return supabase.from('fabric_entries').select('*').eq('id',id).single();}export async function getFabricEntriesWithQuality(){return supabase.from('fabric_entries').select("
      *,
      quality_parameters (*)
    ").order('date_inwarded',{ascending:false});}
